<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/2101207-does-the-book-in-question-exist-roger">Does the book in question exist? Roger de Clinton was in fact Bishop of Coventry in this time period, so it&#39;s conceivable that the book may have been or may be in Coventry. Much was lost in the bombing of the cathedral, so the book could very well be fictitious, but the detailed description makes one wonder.</a>
