<span id="freeTextContainer5203333814306476896">Now we’re back on track! As always, I enjoy Peters’ writing regardless of how disappointing a plot the story has (I’m looking at you, The Confession of Brother Haluin). This one, though, had a surprise element added about halfway through the narrative that ensnared me afresh, and is of a natural to capture the attention of any bibliophile.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


