        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3517670876&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3517670876" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14264695829081343015"><strong>Coveting a book? </strong><br/><br/>After hearing the description of the gift sent as dowry for Fortunata, I too would kill to see it. I&apos;ve always loved well made books and appreciated their worth. I despair of future generations in not having hard-copy versions of stories. I have several &quot;treasures&quot; in my library. But I likely wouldn&apos;t really kill for them.</span>
  <span id="freeText14264695829081343015" style="display:none"><strong>Coveting a book? </strong><br /><br />After hearing the description of the gift sent as dowry for Fortunata, I too would kill to see it. I've always loved well made books and appreciated their worth. I despair of future generations in not having hard-copy versions of stories. I have several "treasures" in my library. But I likely wouldn't really kill for them.</span>
