        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer178888814" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5511023318462889608">William of Lythwood returns from a pilgrimage in a coffin under the care of his apprentice Elave who seeks a burial site at the abbey for his master. Elave is accused of heresy for a statement that he made while in his cups. Brother Cadfael is forced to leave his herb garden to settle matters.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

