<span id="freeTextContainer15238331805643183530">&apos;A Mediaeval Whodunnit&apos; is the subtitle on my edition and that sums it up very nicely. Its a good story, told with all the period detail and fine characterisation you expect from Ellis Peters.<br/>It&apos;s really a 3.5 for me. Good fun to read on holiday and for a light break in between more solid fare.</span>
